{"tid":1507911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益)狗仔狗女防校園欺凌","createTime":"2019-08-26T10:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:58:43.000Z","uid":28433,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c679f0873f146e0b51b663f1755113c072c4755","tid":1507911,"uid":28433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"拿 我就好憎人校園欺凌 不過好人好者點會比人恰<br />\n但係我都要教一眾狗仔狗女點防止果班暴徒亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果大家有方法歡迎一齊提出<br />\n<br />\n煩膠系(精神攻擊)<br />\n1)上pe堂換衫 剪尻爛佢 解決方法:冇<br />\n2)偷尻佢d書或者畫花佢本書 解決方法:冇<br />\n3)倒野入佢書包 e.g.食物 鉛筆碎 解決方法:冇<br />\n4)塞包煙入書包再告比老師知 之後見家長 解決方法:冇<br />\n5)杯葛佢 組隊永遠狗仔同盟 解決方法:冇<br />\n6)係張櫈度痴膠水 解決方法:冇<br />\n-----------------------<br />\n肢體接觸(物理攻擊)<br />\n7)同佢玩 除左對鞋掉撚走佢 解決方法:冇<br />\n8)肢體傷害 解決方法:報警  不過我驚班暴徙蒙哂面伏放學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9)除哂佢d 衫之後放佢走 留條底褲比佢 解決方法:call 狗父救人 不過黎得都可三四十分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10)廁所淋水 解決方法:可以叫老師<br />\n11)happy corner <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />解決方法: 太遲了太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n------------------------<br />\n最高境界精神攻擊 基本下面冇解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼新聞大字報(開名)每個角落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三四條女去老師度講話犬兒露鳥講淫野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈犬兒偷野 塞自己銀包入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞d咸書入書包 or gay圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再大叫要全世界知<br />\n<br />\n幫佢傳上黎本作業寫粗口 or 攝淫野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有咩好提議可以幫下d狗仔狗女免受欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />畢竟用玩下姐呢個籍口真係好難搞 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌 校園欺凌解決方法接近零阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe2abff04b80353bf441eb085057d1926cbd437","tid":1507911,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=3e17abe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=fa101470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102458676557543%2Fposts%2F1582783125191750%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=dab071c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5f88de8a51959f8cb1ce7932a63a313b2d5494a7","tid":1507911,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4G